video.title: Foodgang French restaurant miami beach surfside review by John Lieberman Business coach

Business Coach John Lieberman reviews Food Gang Restaurant Miami Beach Surfside as a business power dining bistro. John talks about the service, french cuisine, appetizers, entres, brunch and the desserts the new chef specializes in. He describes the assortment of wines and wine tastings offered.
